WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.629
Hey, good morning family, praise the Lord.

00:00:02.639 --> 00:00:06.150
Day 51. I'm so thankful you all join

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:09.950
me every day. Yesterday was

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.870
kind of different; I did

00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:14.789
the singing. I don't

00:00:14.799 --> 00:00:16.349
usually sing like that for the whole

00:00:16.359 --> 00:00:18.349
video. I tried to do something a little

00:00:18.359 --> 00:00:20.390
different because I thought they need

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:23.470
to know how to bring in the presence of

00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:25.910
the Lord in their own

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:29.589
house by playing the old songs.

00:00:29.599 --> 00:00:31.150
Y'all, I really believe there's an

00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:33.350
anointing on the older songs—the old

00:00:33.350 --> 00:00:33.360
hymns—the

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:36.190
stuff that wasn't

00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:39.790
trying to make a Dove Award or

00:00:39.790 --> 00:00:39.800
a million-dollar

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:42.790
hit; that was just

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:45.950
pure worship from the heart. I believe

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:50.630
there's something about those songs when

00:00:50.640 --> 00:00:53.150
you sing them that ushers in

00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:55.590
the presence of God in your house. I

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:58.470
think it is vital that we do

00:00:58.480 --> 00:01:00.470
that on a day-to-day basis.

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:01.990
It's kind of

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:03.189
awkward when you're singing in front of

00:01:03.199 --> 00:01:05.390
a camera to thousands

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:08.230
of people and you think, 'Who is

00:01:08.240 --> 00:01:12.109
this guy?'I'm not Celine Dion

00:01:12.119 --> 00:01:15.630
or Luciano Pavarotti or

00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:18.990
Andrea

00:01:18.990 --> 00:01:19.000
Bocelli.

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:22.630
Whatever his name is, I

00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:24.990
just make a

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:26.749
joyful noise to the Lord. I

00:01:26.759 --> 00:01:28.350
appreciate the people who are kind;

00:01:28.360 --> 00:01:30.230
the people who are rude—hey, you try

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:37.230
it. It's not easy. I had some

00:01:37.240 --> 00:01:39.190
things on my heart today to talk about.

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.510
A lot of people were asking

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:44.830
about gold and silver.

00:01:44.840 --> 00:01:47.350
It's fun because it's a tangible

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:49.230
thing whenever you get it; you can

00:01:49.240 --> 00:01:51.230
hold it in your hand.

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:57.029
But people want to know what

00:01:57.029 --> 00:01:57.039
it's

00:01:57.039 --> 00:01:58.709
going to go up to

00:01:58.709 --> 00:01:58.719
and

00:01:58.719 --> 00:02:00.310
what's going to

00:02:00.320 --> 00:02:02.149
happen with it. When I was

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:03.990
praying about gold and silver, I said,

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:06.190
'Lord, what's

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:07.870
going to happen with it?

00:02:07.880 --> 00:02:09.869
Would you give me advice on

00:02:09.869 --> 00:02:09.879
that?'And

00:02:09.879 --> 00:02:11.949
he said,

00:02:11.949 --> 00:02:11.959
'Brandon,

00:02:11.959 --> 00:02:15.550
gold

00:02:15.550 --> 00:02:15.560
will...'—and

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:18.030
everything I say here is not financial

00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:20.390
advice, this is my opinion of what the

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:22.030
Lord has told

00:02:22.040 --> 00:02:24.949
me. You have to pray and ask the Lord

00:02:24.959 --> 00:02:26.589
for yourself. I have to say that as a

00:02:26.599 --> 00:02:28.070
disclaimer because I am not

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:30.070
telling you to invest in or do anything

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:31.630
with your finances concerning gold or

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:34.470
silver; this is for

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:37.589
entertainment purposes only. He

00:02:37.599 --> 00:02:40.309
said, 'Brandon, I want to

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:41.910
talk to you about gold and

00:02:41.910 --> 00:02:41.920
silver.'He

00:02:41.920 --> 00:02:47.070
said to me, 'One day, son, gold

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:48.949
will be an investment that will go to

00:02:48.959 --> 00:02:52.630
over $10,000 an ounce.'I said, 'Wow,

00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:54.430
Lord, that's amazing, but what about

00:02:54.430 --> 00:02:54.440
silver?'I

00:02:54.440 --> 00:02:56.430
said gold was too expensive

00:02:56.440 --> 00:02:57.910
in the natural right now for me

00:02:57.920 --> 00:03:00.350
to purchase.

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:02.430
Silver

00:03:02.440 --> 00:03:05.190
was like $20 or $12 an ounce.

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:09.390
He

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:11.990
said, 'You will see silver go up to about

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:15.550
$40 an ounce, and then it will crash back

00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:19.430
down to about $12 an ounce, and at that

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:21.949
time it would be a good time to purchase

00:03:21.949 --> 00:03:21.959
it.'This

00:03:21.959 --> 00:03:25.350
was back

00:03:25.350 --> 00:03:25.360
in

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:27.429
2014

00:03:27.429 --> 00:03:27.439
or

00:03:27.439 --> 00:03:30.670
2015. He said it

00:03:30.680 --> 00:03:32.830
will go up to about $40 and

00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:35.110
then crash down to about

00:03:35.110 --> 00:03:35.120
$12.

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:37.550
Well, ladies and gentlemen, it did

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:39.509
exactly what he

00:03:39.519 --> 00:03:42.869
said. At $12 an ounce, I was looking

00:03:42.879 --> 00:03:44.869
for those little quarters—1964

00:03:44.869 --> 00:03:44.879
and earlier—and

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:46.509
looking for dimes because

00:03:46.519 --> 00:03:48.429
we could afford

00:03:50.110 --> 00:03:50.120
a

00:03:56.670 --> 00:03:56.680
couple

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:03.270
of

00:04:04.560 --> 00:04:06.550
dimes.

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:11.110
It stayed down there

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:13.750
for a little bit and then gradually

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:15.470
started moving back up again. I think

00:04:15.480 --> 00:04:17.990
it's like $20 right now, but

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:21.030
the Lord told me at that time

00:04:21.030 --> 00:04:21.040
that

00:04:21.040 --> 00:04:25.110
there will be a day when silver

00:04:25.110 --> 00:04:25.120
is

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:30.070
$175 an ounce. He

00:04:30.080 --> 00:04:33.710
said it will never be what

00:04:36.110 --> 00:04:36.120
some

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:40.510
people selling it and

00:04:40.520 --> 00:04:43.749
trying to hype it up think it will be, but

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:48.749
it will be

00:04:48.759 --> 00:04:51.430
a stable thing

00:04:51.430 --> 00:04:51.440
at

00:04:51.440 --> 00:04:55.350
$175 an ounce at some point in time.

00:04:58.639 --> 00:05:01.110
Whenever he talks

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:03.710
to me about things like that,

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:05.510
sometimes it's 10 or 20 years

00:05:05.520 --> 00:05:07.710
away.

00:05:07.720 --> 00:05:10.469
But it

00:05:10.479 --> 00:05:14.230
would not fluctuate like crypto does

00:05:14.230 --> 00:05:14.240
or

00:05:14.240 --> 00:05:16.270
the stock market;

00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:19.469
it's kind of steady

00:05:19.469 --> 00:05:19.479
Eddy.

00:05:19.479 --> 00:05:22.110
As you can see, gold

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:25.270
doesn't bounce

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:27.189
like a rubber ball; it has been

00:05:27.199 --> 00:05:29.189
steady Eddy and it's gradually increased.

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:31.469
Over the course of the last 20 years,

00:05:31.479 --> 00:05:35.110
it hasn't been

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:36.790
something that you've made millions over

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:38.629
like some

00:05:38.639 --> 00:05:41.670
cryptocurrencies, so it's kind of

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:42.790
steady

00:05:42.790 --> 00:05:42.800
Eddy.

00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:45.270
It's for people who don't like

00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:47.350
taking big

00:05:49.309 --> 00:05:49.319
risks.

00:05:51.880 --> 00:05:53.909
I know that at one point in

00:05:53.919 --> 00:05:57.749
time, if you are looking for a

00:05:57.759 --> 00:06:00.550
slight increase, $20 to $175 an

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:03.390
ounce is quite a significant

00:06:03.400 --> 00:06:05.430
turnaround.

00:06:16.520 --> 00:06:18.070
I want to tell you all, when

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:20.990
I say I pray about it, I do not pray to

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:23.749
him about money like that.

00:06:23.759 --> 00:06:26.309
We just

00:06:26.319 --> 00:06:29.189
have casual conversations

00:06:29.199 --> 00:06:32.189
because it says, 'Seek ye first the kingdom,

00:06:32.199 --> 00:06:34.230
and all these things will be added unto

00:06:34.230 --> 00:06:34.240
you.'I

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:37.270
never prostitute the gift like

00:06:37.280 --> 00:06:39.990
that.

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:46.710
He brings it up whenever he wants to

00:06:46.720 --> 00:06:48.550
bring it up.

00:06:52.629 --> 00:06:52.639
You

00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:59.629
might

00:07:03.280 --> 00:07:04.830
say, 'Brandon, I feel like you're off; I

00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:06.550
feel like it's going to be a lot

00:07:06.550 --> 00:07:06.560
less,'or

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:08.309
'I feel like the Lord has

00:07:08.319 --> 00:07:10.189
told me it's going to be at this

00:07:10.189 --> 00:07:10.199
price.'That's

00:07:10.199 --> 00:07:13.070
just what he showed me. I don't

00:07:13.070 --> 00:07:13.080
claim to

00:07:13.080 --> 00:07:15.350
always

00:07:15.350 --> 00:07:15.360
be

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:18.309
right. I believe you

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:20.150
hear the voice of the Lord, and some of

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:22.430
you even better. People

00:07:22.430 --> 00:07:22.440
have asked,

00:07:22.440 --> 00:07:24.710
'Have you heard

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:28.189
anything about Shiba Inu or

00:07:28.189 --> 00:07:28.199
Doge?'I

00:07:28.199 --> 00:07:30.029
have not

00:07:30.039 --> 00:07:32.909
heard anything about those

00:07:32.919 --> 00:07:36.110
cryptocurrencies up until

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:38.309
a couple of weeks ago. He started

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:46.710
bringing names to me and he

00:07:46.710 --> 00:07:46.720
said,

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:49.550
'I want to talk about Doge,'and I

00:07:49.560 --> 00:07:52.430
started praying over Doge, but he never

00:07:52.440 --> 00:07:55.790
told me a price target for that one

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:57.589
yet. I thought it was kind of

00:07:57.599 --> 00:07:59.790
interesting,

00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:06.350
but I don't ever press any

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:08.990
further than that. I let him talk when he

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:11.110
wants to talk.

00:08:11.110 --> 00:08:11.120
I

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:12.749
always have my

00:08:12.759 --> 00:08:15.110
antenna up to listen for

00:08:15.110 --> 00:08:15.120
his

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:18.070
still, small voice.

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:20.550
You have to be in sync and

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:23.670
in step with him on a day-to-day basis.

00:08:23.680 --> 00:08:26.029
You can't be

00:08:26.039 --> 00:08:28.430
in sin and in the

00:08:28.440 --> 00:08:30.869
world and expect God to talk to you

00:08:30.879 --> 00:08:33.190
about

00:08:33.200 --> 00:08:35.469
finances. He has

00:08:35.469 --> 00:08:35.479
to know

00:08:35.479 --> 00:08:37.589
he can

00:08:37.599 --> 00:08:38.709
trust

00:08:38.719 --> 00:08:41.870
you

00:08:41.870 --> 00:08:41.880
with

00:08:41.880 --> 00:08:44.470
when to invest

00:08:44.470 --> 00:08:44.480
and

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:46.389
when not to invest. If you invest

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:48.590
too early, you lose your shirt; if you

00:08:48.600 --> 00:08:50.630
invest too late, you don't get a part

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:54.150
of it. You have to be

00:08:54.160 --> 00:08:57.550
right on target, following the

00:08:57.560 --> 00:08:59.230
voice of the Lord for every single thing

00:08:59.240 --> 00:09:02.350
you do. Too late is too late; too

00:09:02.360 --> 00:09:03.750
early is too

00:09:03.760 --> 00:09:07.110
early.

00:09:07.120 --> 00:09:09.630
Following the voice of the Lord

00:09:09.640 --> 00:09:11.829
concerning investments means following that

00:09:11.839 --> 00:09:13.750
peace that passes

00:09:13.750 --> 00:09:13.760
all

00:09:13.760 --> 00:09:16.590
understanding, not moving by fads

00:09:16.590 --> 00:09:16.600
or

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:19.110
what people say on the internet

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:22.069
concerning gold, silver, or the

00:09:22.079 --> 00:09:25.670
housing market. I heard a story about a man

00:09:25.670 --> 00:09:25.680
who

00:09:25.680 --> 00:09:28.069
had a friend. There was a

00:09:28.079 --> 00:09:30.150
piece of swampy property by a bridge for sale for $3,000. He asked his friends to go in on

00:09:35.829 --> 00:09:35.839
it

00:09:40.920 --> 00:09:43.150
with

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:50.470
him—$1,000

00:09:51.720 --> 00:09:54.590
each. The

00:09:54.590 --> 00:09:54.600
others

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:57.670
said, 'No, I

00:09:57.680 --> 00:10:00.509
don't want that old junk

00:10:00.509 --> 00:10:00.519
land.'But

00:10:00.519 --> 00:10:03.150
one man

00:10:03.160 --> 00:10:05.630
felt inside of his spirit to do

00:10:05.640 --> 00:10:08.110
something, though he didn't obey the

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:10.389
voice of the Lord concerning what he was

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:12.350
supposed to invest

00:10:12.360 --> 00:10:14.990
in. That first guy

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:17.509
bought

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:21.910
it

00:10:24.030 --> 00:10:24.040
for

00:10:28.310 --> 00:10:28.320
$3,000.

00:10:31.160 --> 00:10:32.870
Four or five years

00:10:32.870 --> 00:10:32.880
go

00:10:32.880 --> 00:10:35.750
by,

00:10:35.750 --> 00:10:35.760
and

00:10:35.760 --> 00:10:37.590
the man comes back and

00:10:37.590 --> 00:10:37.600
says,

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:39.470
'Do you remember that old

00:10:39.480 --> 00:10:41.190
trash land?

00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:46.829
The

00:10:46.839 --> 00:10:49.870
state offered

00:10:49.880 --> 00:10:54.269
me $3 million for it because they

00:10:54.279 --> 00:10:55.949
want to put a

00:10:55.959 --> 00:10:57.230
highway through

00:11:00.230 --> 00:11:00.240
there.'He

00:11:02.839 --> 00:11:05.629
made

00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:11.310
a million dollars for every

00:11:11.310 --> 00:11:11.320
thousand

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:14.590
he invested.

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:16.870
They missed out on

00:11:16.880 --> 00:11:19.509
the opportunity

00:12:06.880 --> 00:12:08.470
because they didn't follow the

00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:10.269
voice of

00:12:17.560 --> 00:12:19.110
the Lord. This is how

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:20.990
you practice his presence.

00:12:22.920 --> 00:12:24.590
I was driving

00:12:24.600 --> 00:12:27.030
down

00:12:31.720 --> 00:12:36.230
15th Street

00:12:36.240 --> 00:12:38.470
in Edmond, Oklahoma,

00:12:38.470 --> 00:12:38.480
near

00:12:38.480 --> 00:12:42.030
I-35.

00:12:42.040 --> 00:12:44.509
They're

00:12:44.519 --> 00:12:46.990
building all this area up now with a

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:50.030
Sam's Club, a Chick-fil-A,

00:12:50.040 --> 00:12:51.590
a

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:53.629
Starbucks,

00:12:53.629 --> 00:12:53.639
and

00:12:53.639 --> 00:12:54.949
a

00:12:54.959 --> 00:12:57.230
Walmart.

00:12:57.240 --> 00:13:00.670
There was a piece of property

00:13:00.680 --> 00:13:03.470
about a mile

00:13:03.480 --> 00:13:05.230
down, and as I was

00:13:05.240 --> 00:13:08.310
driving

00:13:10.760 --> 00:13:14.389
West,

00:13:14.399 --> 00:13:16.470
the Lord said, 'Do you

00:13:16.480 --> 00:13:18.230
see that piece of property?

00:13:21.040 --> 00:13:22.430
One day that's going to be worth

00:13:22.440 --> 00:13:24.509
hundreds of millions of

00:13:24.519 --> 00:13:28.189
dollars.'I

00:13:28.199 --> 00:13:30.710
called

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:32.949
the real estate agent because I was curious,

00:13:35.629 --> 00:13:35.639
and

00:13:37.399 --> 00:13:38.710
they

00:13:40.519 --> 00:13:44.550
were asking a million dollars for it. I

00:13:47.920 --> 00:13:51.189
was

00:13:52.519 --> 00:13:55.430
just a janitor at the

00:13:55.440 --> 00:13:57.189
church

00:13:57.199 --> 00:14:00.350
then;

00:14:00.360 --> 00:14:02.550
I didn't have

00:14:02.560 --> 00:14:04.949
the natural means to buy

00:14:04.949 --> 00:14:04.959
million-dollar

00:14:04.959 --> 00:14:07.269
land, but I was learning to

00:14:07.269 --> 00:14:07.279
practice the

00:14:07.279 --> 00:14:08.829
presence of

00:14:08.829 --> 00:14:08.839
the Lord.

00:14:08.839 --> 00:14:12.790
I watched this over the years

00:14:12.800 --> 00:14:14.550
and told my wife and kids,

00:14:14.560 --> 00:14:16.350
'One day that's going to be worth

00:14:17.880 --> 00:14:19.990
a lot of

00:14:21.790 --> 00:14:21.800
money.'Well,

00:14:23.600 --> 00:14:27.430
lo and behold,

00:14:27.430 --> 00:14:27.440
with

00:14:27.440 --> 00:14:28.670
the Sam's

00:14:28.670 --> 00:14:28.680
Club

00:14:29.910 --> 00:14:29.920
and

00:14:29.920 --> 00:14:31.910
everything

00:14:31.920 --> 00:14:33.749
growing up around there,

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:38.870
that

00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:41.749
land has

00:14:41.759 --> 00:14:45.150
houses and shopping centers built all around it. Sometimes

